{"tid":1123734,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"[又到夏天]間房成個天花佈滿呢隻蟲","createTime":"2019-04-24T15:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T04:13:34.000Z","uid":6589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d7e0902f971faa687db670f6f8ddb47f820f008c","tid":1123734,"uid":6589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T15:39:33.000Z","msg":"前排襯住春天涼涼地 開咗隻窗黎訓一排<br />\n<br />\n之後就係惡夢既開始 成個天花板遠睇冇乜野<br />\n<br />\n但近睇就有好多大大細細一隻隻行來行去<br />\n<br />\n呢個月隔一排就抹但抹極都仲有 大既肉眼睇到 <br />\n<br />\n細既要開燈望影先見到踪跡 <br />\n<br />\n間房有隻貓 所以冇得用殺蟲水 <br />\n<br />\n好彩既係貓仔身上冇生呢啲野<br />\n<br />\n都係我衰 明知住村屋仲開窗訓 某程度上自己攞黎<br />\n<br />\n話雖如此 連登有愛 大家有冇對抗呢隻蟲既方法 <br />\n<br />\n懷疑呢排爛面係因為呢啲蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到底呢隻係乜蟲黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vGkEAVm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvGkEAVm.png&h=3f714f65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18bf7b726a92d4bf935372d29750efafba0b013a","tid":1123734,"uid":182624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T15:41:32.000Z","msg":"我用漂白水抹過一排，天氣一濕氣重又出番嚟"},{"pid":"091de61016f930cc53b4c71dc1f50771688794d8","tid":1123734,"uid":5386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T15:52:07.000Z","msg":"一直當佢係bb曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d9c57796894fc0d9df50d713442247aef6cf2e","tid":1123734,"uid":6589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"091de61016f930cc53b4c71dc1f50771688794d8","tid":1123734,"uid":5386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T15:52:07.000Z","msg":"一直當佢係bb曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T15:54:57.000Z","msg":"唔撚係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 張相影到嗰隻係我見到既最大隻 應該唔會係曱甴掛"},{"pid":"c39b98db2a6ead6995e35411972e372dd70d7c53","tid":1123734,"uid":6589,"like":0,"di